msgid "pts"
msgstr "pts"

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Your SEO title should be long enough to explain the topic, but short enough to avoid truncation."
msgstr "Votre titre SEO doit être assez long pour expliquer le sujet, mais assez court pour éviter la troncature."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Aim for about 50–60 characters. Front-load the most important words."
msgstr "Visez environ 50 à 60 caractères. Placez les mots les plus importants en premier."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Clear, visible titles improve click-through rate from search results."
msgstr "Des titres clairs et visibles améliorent le taux de clics à partir des résultats de recherche."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Search engines expect the primary topic to appear in the title."
msgstr "Les moteurs de recherche s'attendent à ce que le sujet principal apparaisse dans le titre."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Include your focus keyphrase naturally near the start of the title."
msgstr "Incluez votre expression-clé cible naturellement près du début du titre."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Improves topical relevance and makes the result more recognizable."
msgstr "Améliore la pertinence thématique et rend le résultat plus reconnaissable."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "A meta description helps search engines and users understand the page."
msgstr "Une méta-description aide les moteurs de recherche et les utilisateurs à comprendre la page."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Write 1–2 sentences that summarize the page and invite a click."
msgstr "Rédigez 1 à 2 phrases qui résument la page et invitent à cliquer."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Better snippets can lift click-through rate even if rankings stay the same."
msgstr "De meilleurs extraits peuvent augmenter le taux de clics même si le classement reste identique."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Descriptions that are too short or too long get cut off in results."
msgstr "Les descriptions trop courtes ou trop longues sont tronquées dans les résultats."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Keep it roughly 140–160 characters and prioritize the main benefit."
msgstr "Gardez environ 140 à 160 caractères et priorisez l'avantage principal."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Full snippets look more professional and improve engagement."
msgstr "Les extraits complets sont plus professionnels et améliorent l'engagement."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Including the focus phrase helps confirm the page topic."
msgstr "Inclure l'expression cible aide à confirmer le sujet de la page."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Work the focus keyphrase into the first sentence naturally."
msgstr "Intégrez l'expression-clé cible dans la première phrase naturellement."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Stronger relevance signals can improve ranking and user confidence."
msgstr "Des signaux de pertinence plus forts peuvent améliorer le classement et la confiance des utilisateurs."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Title and description should not repeat each other."
msgstr "Le titre et la description ne doivent pas se répéter."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Use the title to state the topic and the description to add benefit or context."
msgstr "Utilisez le titre pour énoncer le sujet et la description pour ajouter un avantage ou un contexte."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Distinct messaging gives users more reasons to click."
msgstr "Un message distinct donne aux utilisateurs plus de raisons de cliquer."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Pages should have a single main heading (H1)."
msgstr "Les pages doivent avoir un seul titre principal (H1)."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Keep one H1 that matches the page topic, and use H2/H3 for sections."
msgstr "Conservez un H1 qui correspond au sujet de la page et utilisez H2/H3 pour les sections."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Clear structure helps search engines understand the content hierarchy."
msgstr "Une structure claire aide les moteurs de recherche à comprendre la hiérarchie du contenu."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Subheadings break long content into scannable sections."
msgstr "Les sous-titres divisent le contenu long en sections scannables."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Add 2–8 H2/H3 headings that summarize key sections."
msgstr "Ajoutez 2 à 8 titres H2/H3 qui résument les sections clés."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Improves readability and keeps users engaged longer."
msgstr "Améliore la lisibilité et maintient les utilisateurs engagés plus longtemps."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Including the keyphrase in a subheading reinforces the main topic."
msgstr "Inclure l'expression-clé dans un sous-titre renforce le sujet principal."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Place the focus keyphrase in one relevant H2 or H3."
msgstr "Placez l'expression-clé cible dans un H2 ou H3 pertinent."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Helps search engines connect sections to the main theme."
msgstr "Aide les moteurs de recherche à relier les sections au thème principal."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "The opening paragraph sets context for both users and search engines."
msgstr "Le paragraphe d'ouverture définit le contexte pour les utilisateurs et les moteurs de recherche."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Use the focus keyphrase once in the first 1–2 sentences."
msgstr "Utilisez l'expression-clé cible une fois dans les 1 à 2 premières phrases."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Stronger topical clarity can improve relevance signals."
msgstr "Une plus grande clarté thématique peut améliorer les signaux de pertinence."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Keyphrase density shows how often the main topic appears."
msgstr "La densité d'expression-clé montre à quelle fréquence le sujet principal apparaît."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Use the keyphrase naturally throughout the content without stuffing."
msgstr "Utilisez l'expression-clé naturellement dans tout le contenu sans bourrage."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Balanced usage supports relevance while avoiding spam signals."
msgstr "Une utilisation équilibrée favorise la pertinence tout en évitant les signaux de spam."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Long-tail phrases capture more specific search intent."
msgstr "Les expressions longue traîne capturent une intention de recherche plus spécifique."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Add your long-tail phrases where they fit naturally in sections."
msgstr "Ajoutez vos expressions longue traîne là où elles s'intègrent naturellement dans les sections."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Helps the page rank for more specific queries."
msgstr "Aide la page à se classer pour des requêtes plus spécifiques."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Very short pages often lack depth to satisfy readers."
msgstr "Les pages très courtes manquent souvent de profondeur pour satisfaire les lecteurs."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Expand the content with examples, steps, or FAQs."
msgstr "Développez le contenu avec des exemples, des étapes ou des FAQ."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "More complete content tends to perform better for informational queries."
msgstr "Un contenu plus complet tend à mieux performer pour les requêtes informatives."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Readable content keeps users engaged and reduces bounce."
msgstr "Un contenu lisible maintient l'engagement des utilisateurs et réduit le rebond."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Shorten sentences, use simpler words, and break up long paragraphs."
msgstr "Raccourcissez les phrases, utilisez des mots plus simples et divisez les longs paragraphes."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Improved clarity boosts dwell time and user satisfaction."
msgstr "Une clarté améliorée augmente le temps de séjour et la satisfaction des utilisateurs."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Long sentences are hard to read in CJK languages."
msgstr "Les phrases longues sont difficiles à lire dans les langues CJK."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Split long sentences and add punctuation for clearer flow."
msgstr "Divisez les longues phrases et ajoutez de la ponctuation pour un flux plus clair."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Clearer reading experience helps users stay on the page."
msgstr "Une expérience de lecture plus claire aide les utilisateurs à rester sur la page."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Images support understanding and break up long text."
msgstr "Les images facilitent la compréhension et divisent les longs textes."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Add at least one relevant image that illustrates the topic."
msgstr "Ajoutez au moins une image pertinente qui illustre le sujet."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Visuals improve engagement and can help with image search."
msgstr "Les visuels améliorent l'engagement et peuvent aider à la recherche d'images."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Alt text helps search engines and screen readers interpret images."
msgstr "Le texte alt aide les moteurs de recherche et les lecteurs d'écran à interpréter les images."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
